'''Marc Ribot''' ({{IPAc-en|ˈ|r|iː|b|oʊ}};
born May 21, 1954) is an American guitarist and composer.

His work has touched on many styles, including [[no wave]], [[free jazz]], [[Rock music|rock]], and [[Cuban music]]. Ribot is also known for collaborating with other musicians, most notably [[Tom Waits]], [[Elvis Costello]], [[Vinicio Capossela]] and [[John Zorn]].
